<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="js" lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta content="width=device-width" name="viewport">
    <title>Add claim: Permanent Impairment | MyService</title>
    <link href="docs/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="uikit-body uikit-grid uikit-refactor">
    <noscript>
        <p role="alert">This website needs JavaScript to work properly.</p>
    </noscript>
    <nav class="uikit-skip-link">
        <a class="uikit-skip-link__link" href="#main-content">Skip to main content</a>
    </nav>
    <% include ../../../global/partials/header-topbar.ejs %>
        <% include ../../../global/partials/header-claims.ejs %>
            <% include ../partials/help-button.ejs %>
                <main>
                    <div class="container" id="main-content">
                        <div id="progressbar">
                            <div id="percentage"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h1 class="margin-below--mid">
                            <span class="heading">Mobility</span>
                        </h1>

                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-9">
                                    <h3 class="margin-below">Tell us how your mobility is affected by your approved conditions so that we can determine
                                        your level of compensation.
                                        <span class="hint">Answer based on your worst day.</span>
                                    </h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-9 margin-below--extra action-group" style="border-top:3px solid #cccccc; border-bottom:3px solid #cccccc; padding-top:3em; padding-bottom:3em;">
                                    <legend class="legend-label margin-below--none">Complete the statement</b>
                                    </legend>
                                    <label for="mobility" style="font-weight:normal;">The affect my conditions have on my mobility is &nbsp;</label>
                                    <span class="mys-dropdown">
                                        <select class="uikit-text-input mys-dropdown__select" id="mobility" name="mobility">
                                            <option value="">Choose an option</option>
                                            <option value="minimal">minimal</option>
                                            <option value="low">low</option>
                                            <option value="mild">mild</option>
                                            <option value="moderate">moderate</option>
                                            <option value="high">high</option>
                                            <option value="veryhigh">very high</option>
                                            <option value="extreme">extreme</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </span>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-minimal">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>minimal</b> affect is a slight effect on your mobility.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>The effects are at irregular intervals and between these affects there are
                                                    no restrictions. For example, migrains or panic attacks.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-low">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>low</b> affect is a minor effect on your mobility.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example, slowing of pace at times or need for a walking stick on occasion.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-mild">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>mild</b> affect is a small reduction in your mobility.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example trouble with balance, dependancy on a walking stick or mild anxiety.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-moderate">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>moderate</b> affect is a considerable reduction in your mobility.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example you have a substantial amount of difficulty with activities around
                                                    the house or getting to and from places.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-high">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>high</b> affect is a major reduction in your mobility.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example you are dependant on others or aids, or you are unable to use
                                                    public transport without assistance.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-veryhigh">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>A
                                                <b>very high</b> affect is a severe reduction in your mobility.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example, you are restricted to your home unless assistance is provided,
                                                    or you are unable to drive.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="action-group__reveal--closed" id="mobility-extreme">
                                        <div class="uikit-page-alerts uikit-page-alerts--info">
                                            <p>An
                                                <b>extreme</b> affect is a critical reduction in your mobility.
                                                <br>
                                                <i>For example you are restricted to you home permanently, or you are fully
                                                    dependant on others and aids.</i>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- <div class="row margin-below">
                                <div class="col-sm-12">
                                    <h3>Now tell us some more stuff</h3>
                                </div>
                            </div> -->

                            <div class="row margin-below">
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-5">
                                    <legend class="legend-label">Do you have trouble with certain daily activities that you used to be able to do?
                                        <span class="hint display-block">For example driving, walking or socialising.</span>
                                    </legend>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="mys-radio-group">
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="pi-questions" value="no">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">No</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="pi-questions" value="yes-a-little">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes, a little</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="pi-questions" value="yes-a-lot">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes, a lot</span>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row margin-below">
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-5">
                                    <legend class="legend-label">Do you need the assisstance of an aid to help get around?
                                        <span class="hint display-block">For example a wheelchair, walking stick or assistance animal.</span>
                                    </legend>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="mys-radio-group">
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="aid" value="no">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">No</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="aid" value="yes-a-little">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes, a little</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="aid" value="yes-a-lot">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes, a lot</span>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row margin-below">
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-5">
                                    <legend class="legend-label">Do you feel uncomfortable travelling without assistance?</legend>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <div class="mys-radio-group">

                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="transport" value="no">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">No</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="transport" value="yes-a-little">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes, a little</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="transport" value="yes-a-lot">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes, a lot</span>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row margin-below--extra border-bottom">
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-5">
                                    <legend class="legend-label">Does your condition restrict you to your home?</legend>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 margin-below--extra">
                                    <div class="mys-radio-group">
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="home" value="no">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">No</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="home" value="yes-a-little">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes, a little</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <label class="mys-radio">
                                            <input class="mys-radio__control" type="radio" name="home" value="yes-a-lot">
                                            <span class="mys-radio__box">Yes, a lot</span>
                                        </label>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-sm-12">
                                    <fieldset>
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                            <label class="uikit-text-input__label" for="textArea">Tell us more.
                                                <span class="hint display-block">This will help us to better understand how your approved conditions have
                                                    affected your mobility.
                                                </span>
                                            </label>
                                            <textarea id="textArea" name="statementText" rows="6"></textarea>
                                        </div>
                                    </fieldset>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>






                        <div class="pagination">
                            <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/pi-claim1'">Previous</button>
                            <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '#open-modal'">Cancel claim</button>
                            <div class="floated">
                                <button class="uikit-btn uikit-btn--tertiary" onclick="window.location.href = '/pi-claim1'">Save and exit</button>&nbsp;
                                <button class="uikit-btn btnNext" id="btnNext" onclick="window.location.href = '/pi-claim3'">Save and next</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% include ../partials/cancel-modal.ejs %>
                    </div>

                </main>

                <% include ../../../global/partials/footer.ejs %>
                    <% include ../partials/panel-help.ejs %>

                        <script>

                            // Progress percentage

                            document.getElementById("percentage").style.width = "33.2%";

                            // Dynamic content for mobility rating drop-down
                            $("#mobility").change(function () {
                                // minimal
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "minimal") {
                                    $("#mobility-minimal").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-minimal").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-minimal").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-minimal").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // low
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "low") {
                                    $("#mobility-low").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-low").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-low").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-low").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // mild
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "mild") {
                                    $("#mobility-mild").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-mild").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-mild").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-mild").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // moderate
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "moderate") {
                                    $("#mobility-moderate").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-moderate").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-moderate").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-moderate").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // high
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "high") {
                                    $("#mobility-high").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-high").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-high").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-high").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // very high
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "veryhigh") {
                                    $("#mobility-veryhigh").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-veryhigh").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-veryhigh").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-veryhigh").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                                // extreme
                                if ($('#mobility :selected').val() == "extreme") {
                                    $("#mobility-extreme").removeClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                    $("#mobility-extreme").addClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                } else {
                                    $("#mobility-extreme").removeClass('action-group__reveal--open');
                                    $("#mobility-extreme").addClass('action-group__reveal--closed');
                                }
                            });

                        </script>

</body>

</html>